headline: HCA Healthcare (HCA) Beats Q4 Earnings Estimates
summary: HCA (HCA) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +8.90% and -0.63%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
